name: Porsche 911
description: The Porsche 911 is the brand’s most iconic rear-engine sports car, renowned for its timeless design, exceptional handling, and heritage in motorsports.

name: Porsche Cayenne
description: The Cayenne is Porsche’s luxury midsize SUV that blends sports car performance with everyday practicality and comfort.

name: Porsche Taycan
description: The Taycan is Porsche’s first all-electric vehicle, delivering exhilarating performance, advanced tech, and Porsche DNA in a futuristic EV package.

name: Porsche Panamera
description: The Panamera is a luxury performance sedan that combines Porsche’s sporty driving experience with four-door comfort and cutting-edge features.

name: Porsche Macan
description: The Porsche Macan is a compact luxury SUV offering dynamic handling, sporty design, and premium interior—ideal for daily driving and weekend fun.
